    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle presents in showroom condition, having been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled environment since new. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, dings, or rock chips, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no visible wear on the bolsters, and the interior retains its original factory freshness. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history documented from day one, with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is a collector-grade specimen that drives as tightly and smoothly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The sale includes all original keys, manufacturer manuals, and a bespoke car cover.",
